Don't mind me and my casual deck, but some well reasoned tech options/niche play suggestions would be cool. Leaning more towards banishing and recycle plays with the Pot of Acquisitiveness and Nemeses Engine. I don't have IRL access to Pot of Prosperity because I have no luck in opening packs and 1 copy costing $100 is nuts (also I hate giving up access to flexibility options in my Extra Deck).

Like I said, any other tech suggestions geared toward the banishing mechanic would be appreciated

